Package chav1961.funnypro.core.interfaces

This package contains all important interfaces for the Funny prolog core

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FProPluginList
    This interface describes descriptor of external plugins in the system
    IFProAskEntity
    This interface describes asked FPro entities
    IFProEntitiesRepo
    This interface supports entities repo functionality
    IFProEntitiesRepo.SerializableString
    This interface describes content of the string and term trees in the FProVM database
    IFProEntity
    This interface describes FPro entities
    IFProExternalEntity
    This interface describes FPro external entities
    IFProExternalPluginsRepo
    This interface describes all external plugins in the system
    IFProExternalPluginsRepo.ExternalEntityDescriptor
    The interface describes resolver for external entities
    IFProExternalPluginsRepo.PluginDescriptor
    This interface describes one external plugin in the system
    IFProExternalPluginsRepo.PluginItem
    This interface describes one external plugin item in the system
    IFProGlobalStack
    This interface describes global stack
    IFProGlobalStack.AndChainStackTop
    This interface describes common AND node of the expression
    IFProGlobalStack.BoundStackTop<T>
    This interface describes any binded data list as a result of unification process
    IFProGlobalStack.ExternalStackTop
    This interface describes external predicate placed in the stack
    IFProGlobalStack.GlobalStackTop
    This interface describes common stack top element
    IFProGlobalStack.IteratorStackTop<T>
    This interface describes any data iterator in the stack
    IFProGlobalStack.OrChainStackTop
    This interface describes common OR node of the expression
    IFProGlobalStack.TemporaryStackTop
    This interface describes any temporary data placed in the stack
    IFProList
    This interface describes FPro list entities
    IFProModule
    This interface describes the minimal functionality for the modules
    IFProMutableOperator
    This interface extends operator description with it's mutability
    IFProOperator
    This interface describes FPro operator definitions
    IFProParserAndPrinter
    This interface supports parsing and printing for the FPro entities
    IFProParserAndPrinter.FProParserCallback
    This interface describes callback for processing goals and questions
    IFProPluginManager
    This interface describes FProVM external plugin manager
    IFProPredicate
    This interface describes predicate definitions
    IFProQuickList<D>
    This interface describes quick array-based ordered list to use
    IFProRepo
    This interface describes FPro repository.
    IFProRepo.NameAndArity
    This interface describes all the entity types in the fact/rule base
    IFProRuledEntity
    This interface describes any ruled entity
    IFProSettings
    This interface collects configuration keys
    IFProStreamSerializable
    THis interface describes stream serializable items
    IFProStringRepo
    This interface collects all strings
    IFProStringSerializable
    This interface describes string serializable items
    IFProVariable
    This interface describes FPro list entities
    IFProVM
    This interface describes IFPro VM
    IFProVM.IFProCallback
    This is a callback interface for the resolutions
    IResolvable
    This interface describes any external predicates/operators plugin.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IFProEntitiesRepo.Classification
    This enumeration is used to classify terms detected by the term tree: operator - term is operator term - term is ordinal term anonymous - term is anonymous variable variable - term is variable op - term is :- op/3 exterm - term is external predicate description
    IFProEntity.EntityType
    This enumerations describes FPro entity type: string - string term integer - integer term real - real term anonymous - anonymous variable variable - variable externalplugin - external plugin description list - list item operatordef - :- op/3 operator - any operator predicate - any predicate
    IFProGlobalStack.StackTopType
    This enumeration describes content of the global stack top: andChain - AND node of the expression orChain - OR node of the expression iterator - any expression source bounds - binded variable list temporary - temporary data
    IFProOperator.OperatorType
    This enumeration describes operator types
    IResolvable.ResolveRC
    This enumeration describes return codes from resolving results.
